description: The Fund seeks to track the performance of an index composed of Sterling denominated investment grade corporate bonds.*Please note that as of 1 October 2015, the benchmark index for the fund changed from the Markit iBoxx GBP Corporates 1-5 Index to the Markit iBoxx GBP Corporates 0-5 Index.
name: iShares Corp Bond 0-5yr UCITS ETF
